Package com.orchestranetworks.addon.dmdv.data.label

Provides the interfaces and classes to define the label for a link or node.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LinkLabelContext
    Gets the data required for a renderer.
    LinkLabelRenderer
    Defines a label renderer that depends on the currently evaluated link.
    NodeLabelContext
    Gets the data required for the label renderer.
    NodeLabelRenderer
    Defines a label renderer that depends on the currently evaluated node.

Package com.orchestranetworks.addon.dmdv.data.label Description

Provides the interfaces and classes to define the label for a link or node. An administrator can include the custom label render in a link configuration or node configuration. See the Developers Guide for more information.
